Cell["\<\
of two different generators may (falsely) suggest that the restriction is not \
decomposed. In fact, just change of ordering confirms that the restriction is \
decomposed:\
\>", "TechNoteText",
 CellID->502819390,ExpressionUUID->"a1791764-027f-414e-ad7a-102fb0b9219a"],

