Cell["\<\
The restriction of the above irreducible representation of U(3) to subgroup \
U(2) is reducible and is decomposed into different irreducible \
representations of U(2):\
\>", "TechNoteMathCaption",
 CellID->93094172,ExpressionUUID->"dba4bf9d-72cb-4eca-81fd-b277d375f302"],

