Cell["\<\
are conventionally regarded equivalent, but within the formulation of \
branching rules (e.g., for a subgroup adapted basis), they are regarded as \
inequivalent since they originate in different partitions, namely, (2,1) and \
(1), before adding the boxes with entry 3.\
\>", "TechNoteText",
 CellID->1138128981,ExpressionUUID->"59df361f-5808-4ec0-b444-47270bcc7cf3"],

